<HEADLINE> Zimbabwe Refutes UK Criticism </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Shamuyarira, who is also Secretary for Information and
Publicity of the ruling Zimbabwe African National Union-Patriotic
Front (Zanu-pf), was responding to a recent report published in a
London newspaper which said a group of British and American
politicians and businessmen were funding the opposition Movement
for Democratic Change (MDC) to topple President Mugabe' s
government from power.
</P>
<P>
The minister said the information being spread to other western
 countries by Britain was biased against Zimbabwe and Zanu-pf in
particular.
</P>
<P>
