<HEADLINE> Tibet Values Cultural Relics Preservation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LHASA, May 24 (Xinhua) -- Tibet attaches importance to
preserving its cultural relics in the course of economic
development, Yang Xiaodu, vice chairman of the Tibet Autonomous
