<HEADLINE> Earthquake Hits Liaoning Province </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHENYANG, May 24 (Xinhua) -- An earthquake measuring 4.3 on the
Richter scale jolted the area between Xiuyan and Haicheng in
northeast China's Liaoning Province at 7:44 am (Beijing time)
today.
</P>
