Movement since the beginning of May, the local radio reported.
</P>
<P>
About 800 militiamen surrendered this week when the Israeli-
allied militia collapsed with Israel's withdrawal from south
Lebanon. ( Lebanon-SLA-Surrender)
</P>
<P>
- - - -
</P>
<P>
WASHINGTON -- The United States said Tuesday that it wanted
Lebanese army to take over southern Lebanon in an orderly way
after Israel pulls its troops back from the occupied area.
</P>
<P>
