<HEADLINE> Dalian to Host Intl. Art Expo </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DALIAN, May 24 (Xinhua) -- The 2000 Dalian Art Expo will be
held in August in this coastal city of northeast China's Liaoning
Province.
</P>
<P>
On display during the expo, sponsored by the Chinese Artists'
Association and the city's federation of literary and art circles,
will be an abundance of art works from galleries in a dozen
countries and regions, including China, the United States, France,
Italy and Russia.
</P>
<P>
The expo will feature traditional Chinese paintings, oil
paintings, prints, handicrafts, pottery, calligraphic works, and
sculpture, said a local cultural official. A series of art
seminars, contests and exhibitions will also be held during the
event.  
</P>
