</P>
<P>
-- A signed commentary, titled "One-China Principle Is Not
Saddled on Taiwan", criticizes the May 20 speech by new Taiwan
leader for his not clearly recognizing the One-China Principle.
</P>
<P>
The commentary reiterates the mainland's stance that everything
is negotiable within the framework of the One-China principle.
</P>
<P>
