on Compensation in Floodwater-Storing Areas and Draft Amendments
on the Fishery Law.
</P>
<P>
The two drafts were approved at the 28th executive meeting of
the Chinese cabinet, which was presided over by Premier Zhu Rongji.
</P>
<P>
 China Daily
</P>
<P>
-- The new Modern Chinese Literature Archives was officially
opened Tuesday and President Jiang Zemin inscribed the name of the
archives.
</P>
<P>
-- Chinese Foreign Ministry spokeswoman Zhang Qiyue Tuesday
called on the U.S. House of Representatives to grant China
unconditionally the status of permanent normal trade relations and
told Taiwan leader to accept the one-China principle.  
