border, is not a demarcation of the border, and other elements,
including the disbanding of the South Lebanon Army would also have
to be verified.
</P>
<P>
According to reports reaching here, the last of Israeli
soldiers in southern Lebanon have returned home today, ending a
military occupation that lasted for 22 years.
</P>
<P>
U.N. Secretary-General Kofi Annan on Monday recommended to
reinforce UNIFIL so as to verify the Israeli withdrawal and to
maintain the situation there. 
